    <note type="biography">
        <p>Physician and journal editor. Graduate of Queen’s University, Belfast. Lecturer in histology, St Mary’s Hospital, London. Editor of the <hi rend="italic">Monthly Microscopical Journal</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Scientific Opinion</hi>, and <hi rend="italic">Popular Science Review.</hi> Published on the treatment of neuralgia with injections of morphia, based on his own case.</p></note>
    <note type="sources">
        <p>Barton 1998, pp. 6 and 16</p>
